OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,6,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,7,Fwill brighten in the south during the
OL,8,Fafternoon with some hazy spells of
OL,9,Fsunshine possible later. Near normal
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining largely cloudy
OL,13,Fovernight, perhaps with a few breaks
OL,14,Fin the cloud here and there. Further
OL,15,Foutbreaks of patchy drizzle likely
OL,16,Fespecially over the hills of Cumbria.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
