OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many on
OL,6,FTuesday with further patchy drizzle.
OL,7,FHowever the cloud will lift and break
OL,8,Fmore readily during the afternoon with
OL,9,Fa strengthening southwesterly wind.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FIncreasingly changeable from
OL,13,FWednesday, with showers or longer
OL,14,Fspells of rain. Some sunny spells are
OL,15,Falso likely, with temperatures near
OL,16,Fnormal, but turning colder by Friday.
OL,17,FWindy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
